Type: Package
Package: PhilipsHue
Title: R Interface to the Philips Hue API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person('Justin', 'Brantley', email = 'fascinatingfingers@icloud.com', role = c('aut', 'cre'))
Description: The PhilipsHue package provides an R interface to the Philips Hue
    API service, making it easy to make API calls and process the response into
    convenient, R-friendly data structures. See
    <https://developers.meethue.com/philips-hue-api> for the Philips Hue API
    Documentation.
